0:05:54.960,0:05:59.820
In the case of Jesus, once you receive something from Him,

0:05:59.820,0:06:02.720
He should be the One to maintain it for you.

0:06:02.720,0:06:06.060
If not, you will loose it.

0:06:06.060,0:06:09.820
This is why we run helter-skelter today.

0:06:09.820,0:06:14.360
You were there yesterday but where are you today?

0:06:14.360,0:06:16.000
You think you can rob Him.

0:06:16.000,0:06:22.200
It's all for the salvation of your soul.

0:06:22.200,0:06:25.820
Be ready to stay with Him for maintenance.

0:06:25.820,0:06:29.440
You lack maintenance;
stay with Him for maintenance.

0:06:29.440,0:06:30.140
Tell your neighbour.

0:06:30.140,0:06:32.020
Stay with Him for maintenance.

0:06:32.020,0:06:32.680
Again.

0:06:32.680,0:06:34.680
Stay with Him for maintenance.

